To the fixing of the extended object types will(_be) the  top, unused Byte of
OB_TYPE uses\ed. The  assignment agrees with it nearly the  Flydials of Julian
Reschke i.e.. the  Mydials of Olaf Meisiek. Through it can the  dialogues already
in INTERFACE over 'object tree test' with its later Look become depicted.


In the  following overview are in each case the  extended type,that  original(ly)
object type and the  set flag given:

-
17 'FlyDial' (IBOX)
 OUTLINED, CROSSED

 The  object in the  top right corner of a dialogues, with that the 
 dialogue-box can become moved. 

-
18 Radiobutton (BUTTON or STRING)
 SELECTABLE, RBUTTON

 A round Radiobutton.

-
18 Checkbox (BUTTON)
 Not EXIT

 A small box(es) with a cross. Is the  flag CHECKED, but not SELECTED,
 placed, will(_be) the  small box(es) with a Punktmuster stuffed. With it lets
 (self) a so-called. "Tristate-Button" manage. See to it too the  Routine
 'rsc_tristate' in the  extended routines and the  which goes with it text.

-
18 Exitbutton (BUTTON)
 EXIT

 A 'normal' Button,that  but over the  keyboard can become serves\ed. 

-
18 String (STRING)
 TOUCHEXIT

 A keyboard-operable String. If the  next to object a Popup-is
 Button, so can with this the  Popup become opened.

-
19 Unterstrichener text (BUTTON or STRING)

 Becomes normally for the  title of 1 form employs\ed. The  length
 of the  underline will(_be) through the  width of the  object decides\ed.

-
20 frame (BUTTON)

 A frame with a text in the  left top corner.

-
21 Niceline (STRING)
 DISABLED

 Only in Dropdown-menus meaningful: The  separating lines '-' become
 umgestaltet. Nicelines are too in Popup-menus usable.
 Reference: With the  Mydials marks/ed the  type 21 a HELP-Button.
 I soft in this a point from it from, there so the  initialization
 accelerates\ed will(_be).

-
22 Circlebutton (BOXCHAR)
 TOUCHEXIT

 Becomes through a small circle depicted and serves in the connection
 with a popup menu to the Weiterschalten of the menu entry.
 Reference: Want you the  Circlebutton as\than 'normal' object without
 connection to a Popup-menu employ, so should it through a different
 object (e.g. BOX) become be inferior.

-
31 Popup-Button (BOXTEXT)
 SHADOWED

 The  Button,that  a Popup-menu appear lets. The  differentiation to
 Popup-Button will(_be) though not with the help of the  extended object type,
 but on the Status SHADOWED festgemacht. In the unbenutzen Byte of OB_TYPE
 will(_be) the  Index of the  Popups plus 30 held down, see below.

-

